The '''Magnificent''' was a title used of [[Meriadoc Brandybuck]] after his return from the [[War of the Ring]].<ref>{{App|Later}}</ref><ref>{{App|Brandybuck}}</ref>

The [[Thranduil|Elvenking]] called [[Bilbo Baggins]] "Bilbo the Magnificent" when Bilbo before departing gave him a present as a return for his "hospitality".<ref>{{H|18}}.</ref>

